Package model.uPickBingo

Class UPickBingoCell

java.lang.Object
model.uPickBingo.UPickBingoCell
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cell
public class UPickBingoCell extends Object implements Cell
A class defining a UPick Bingo cell that can be used with a card of the same game. Implements the Cell interface, providing the necessary functionality for a UPick Bingo cell, including state management, marking, and highlighting.
Version:
1.1.0 - May 2024
Author:
Lucia Andronic
